What will be the default values of all the elements of an array defined as an instance variable?
Data Type	Default Value
byte	0
short	0
int	0
long	0L
float	0.0f
double	0.0d
char	'\u0000' (null character)
boolean	false
Reference types (String, Objects)	null

Important interview point ‚≠ê
‚úÖ Instance variables ‚Üí auto-initialized
‚ùå Local variables ‚Üí NOT auto-initialized (compiler error if used without assignment)
